    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "This Bureau's Office at Phoenix, Arizona, received",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "from the [REDACTED] Arizona, a form letter which he",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "received from [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Hill, London, N. 16, England. The envelope containing the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "form letter was postmarked \"Stoke, Newington, 10-26-54.\" The",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "form letter with a typewritten note bearing the signature of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED], who identified himself as \"Aerial Phenomena",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Investigator,\" seeks information regarding the sighting of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "flying saucers. [REDACTED] indicated that the purpose of his",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "inquiry was \"in order to bring my reports and filing system",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "up to date it would be very much appreciated if you would",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "kindly complete the enclosed form and return same to me.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The form calls for the following type data concerning",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "any flying saucers observed: \"Time of sighting, size, shape,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "composition, speed, altitude, direction, manoeuvre pattern, color,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "sound, length of time observed, sky conditions, visibility,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "direction of ground wind.\" On the form is provided a space for",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "the name, age and address of the person executing the form and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "a space for general remarks.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
